    narr:generatedFrom "6eaa3515d21bb5def185a38ce1990054cb129646" ;
    narr:narration """This hub tracks the evolution of the system's rhetorical architecture, where technical domains are consistently mapped onto narrative and cognitive processes. The core physics-based framing—narrative as a [steering vector](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_SteeringVector) for generative systems—has expanded into a kinetic, directional idiom, notably the [archery/arrow metaphor](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_EVFlocking_ArrowMetaphor) used to describe iterative aim. The [optometrist model](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_OptometristMetaphor) remains the primary UX anchor, while infrastructure analogies continue to dominate: [Git-based collaboration](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_GitMetaphor), [OS-level program installation](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_ModelAsOSMetaphor), and the [white-space collapse](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_WhiteSpaceCollapse) of organizational perspective. Recent entries introduce more visceral, high-stakes imagery, such as the [raven metaphor](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_DiscoveryWedge_MetaphorRaven) for avoiding premature focus, and spatial metaphors like the [castle tour](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_CastleMetaphor) for IP disclosure. The corpus also documents a shift toward borrowing engineering primitives—[closures, channels, and atomic writes](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_SelfServe_TechnicalMetaphor)—to describe product design, signaling a move toward treating organizational memory as [executable code](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_EngineeringMetaphor).""" ;
